To facilitate writing out blurb for each variant of a ship, as until now they've been left blank, I've created some templates containing standard blurb. To add the blurb, then the following wikitext is used;

<pre>
==Variants==
===Regular===
{{regular}}
===Advanced===
{{advanced}}
...
etc
</pre>

Feel free to add some specific blurb in place of (or in additon to) the standard.

